name: Morgan D Franco
description: I’m new to this online dating thing, but my friends tell me it’s the way to go. So here goes. I’m a professional and responsible guy looking to meet a responsible woman. I love the beach. I enjoy dining out, dancing, the movies and taking strolls on the beach, preferably with an attractive female companion. I’m recently divorced and not unhappy about being single. . I enjoy the going out, especially places with live music, but I’m also giving this internet thing a shot. I would really like to meet someone new to share my life and have fun. I believe that once you’ve met me, at the very least ..you would like me. So why not give us a chance to find out if there is any chemistry here. You can’t light a fire without a spark !!!
